title: Danny & Billy Eichner (BROS)
itunes:title: Danny & Billy Eichner (BROS)
description:
Danny chats with star and co-writer of the new movie BROS, Billy Eichner! They discuss the wonderful new film, Billy on the Street, Difficult People, working with Queen Mariah Carey, what's next for Billy, favorite romcoms, Renée Zellweger's filmography, and so much more!
